Parse¶

$project will solve your problem of where to start with documentation, by providing a basic explanation of how to do it easily.

Look how easy it is to use:

import project
# Get your stuff done
project.do_stuff()

Output Format¶

{
"course": "name",
}

{
	"course": "EN.600.200"
}

Features¶

  • Be awesome
  • Make things faster

Installation¶

Install $project by running:

install project
